Summary

Dataset: Bangladesh

Outcome variable: Emergent Numeracy (size1 - puzzle)

Comparison variable: Treatment Condition (control, treatment)

Items with no variance: none

Items with no variance within levels of comparison variable: none

Bias detection method: IRT

Total number of biased items: 6 out of 28

Type of item bias: uniform

  • Number of items uniformly biased toward control: 0

  • Number of items uniformly biased toward treatment: 6
